Micri-M Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy describes how Micri-M collects, uses, and processes data about you.
By using our apps, you agree to the collection and use of your data in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
We do not use or share your data with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
Data we collect
• App Info and Performance
We may collect crash logs and diagnostics data for the following purposes:
- Analytics
- Advertising or marketing
- Fraud prevention, security, and compliance
• App Activity
We may collect interactions with the app for the following purposes:
- Analytics
- Advertising or marketing
- Fraud prevention, security, and compliance
• Device or Other IDs
We may collect the Android advertising ID, app set ID, device metadata, Crashlytics installation UUID, Analytics App-instance ID, and Firebase Android App ID for the following purposes:
- Analytics
- Advertising or marketing
- Fraud prevention, security, and compliance
- Personalization
Data retention
We retain data associated with advertising identifiers on Google Analytics for 14 months, this doesn't affect most standard reporting, which is based on aggregated data.
Firebase retains Firebase installation IDs, this data is removed from live and backup systems within 180 days.
Firebase Crashlytics retains crash stack traces, extracted minidump data, and associated identifiers (including Crashlytics Installation UUIDs) for 90 days.
Note: Firebase Crashlytics stores minidump data only temporarily in order to process NDK crashes.
Data handling and security
We and our service providers use industry standard security practices to protect your data in transit and at rest. All data is transferred over a secure connection using HTTPS.
Data deletion
You can request us to delete the data we have collected about you by contacting us at:
email
The Android ad ID can be reset or deleted by you using ad ID controls in the Android settings menu.
Contact us
For all data privacy inquiries and any questions or concerns you have about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
email
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our information practices. Any updates or changes to this Policy will be published here.
